time to treatment progression was >9 weeks. Median overall survival was 397 
days. An increase in the expression of interferon-γ was not significant.
CONCLUSIONS: Therapy was safe. The responses, time to treatment progression and 
survival are encouraging for patients with aggressive refractory disease.

