Physical precipitating factors in functional movement disorders.

Pareés I(1), Kojovic M(2), Pires C(3), Rubio-Agusti I(4), Saifee TA(3), Sadnicka 
A(3), Kassavetis P(3), Macerollo A(5), Bhatia KP(3), Carson A(6), Stone J(6), 
Edwards MJ(3).

Author information:
(1)Sobell Department of Motor Neuroscience and Movement Disorders, UCL Institute 
of Neurology, Queen Square, London, UK. Electronic address: 
isabel.parees-moreno.10@ucl.ac.uk.
(2)Sobell Department of Motor Neuroscience and Movement Disorders, UCL Institute 
of Neurology, Queen Square, London, UK; Department of Neurology, University of 
